Yes, creating a custom template tags file is a good solution if you want to use the `with` template tag in multiple templates across your Django project.

Here are the steps to create a custom template tags file and register the `with` tag:

1. Create a new directory called `templatetags` inside your Django app directory (e.g., `contest/templatetags`).

2. Inside the `templatetags` directory, create a new Python file, e.g., `custom_tags.py`.

3. In the `custom_tags.py` file, add the following code:

```python
from django import template
register = template.Library()

@register.tag
def with_(parser, token):
    """
    Allows the use of the 'with' statement in templates.
    """
    bits = token.split_contents()
    if len(bits) != 3:
        raise template.TemplateSyntaxError("%r tag requires two arguments" % bits[0])
    value = parser.compile_filter(bits[2])
    args = [
        parser.compile_filter(bits[1]),
        value,
    ]
    return WithNode(*args)

class WithNode(template.Node):
    def __init__(self, var, value):
        self.var = var
        self.value = value

    def render(self, context):
        context[self.var.var] = self.value.resolve(context)
        return ''
```

This code defines a custom template tag `with_` that allows you to use the `with` statement in your templates.

4. In your Django app's `templates` directory, create a new directory called `templatetags` (e.g., `contest/templates/templatetags`).

5. Inside the `templatetags` directory, create an empty file named `__init__.py`. This file is required for Django to recognize the directory as a Python package.

6. In your template file (e.g., `user_predictions.html`), load the custom template tags by adding the following line at the top of the file:

```html
{% load custom_tags %}
```

7. Now you can use the `with_` tag in your template file instead of the `with` tag:

```html
{% load custom_tags %}
{% extends 'base.html' %}

{% block content %}
<h2>Wszystkie typy</h2>

<div class="user-predictions">
    {% for data in user_data %}
    <div class="card">
        <h3>{{ data.user.username }}</h3>

        <h4>Mecze:</h4>
        <table class="prediction-table">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Gospodarze</th>
                <th>Gole gospodarzy</th>
                <th>Gole goci</th>
                <th>Gocie</th>
                <th>Wynik</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            {% for bet in data.bets %}
            {% if bet.match.actualresults %}
            {% with_ actual=bet.match.actualresults %}
            {% with_ is_exact_score=actual.home_team_score == bet.home_team_score and actual.away_team_score == bet.away_team_score %}
            {% with_ is_correct_result=(actual.home_team_score > actual.away_team_score and bet.home_team_score > bet.away_team_score) or (actual.home_team_score < actual.away_team_score and bet.home_team_score < bet.away_team_score) or (actual.home_team_score == actual.away_team_score and bet.home_team_score == bet.away_team_score) %}
            <tr>
                <td>{{ bet.match.home_team }}</td>
                <td>{{ bet.home_team_score }}</td>
                <td>{{ bet.away_team_score }}</td>
                <td>{{ bet.match.away_team }}</td>
                <td class="{% if is_exact_score %}
                            exact-score
                            {% elif is_correct_result %}
                            correct-result
                            {% else %}
                            wrong-result
                            {% endif %}">
                    {% if is_exact_score %}
                    <span>Trafiony dokadny wynik</span>
                    {% elif is_correct_result %}
                    Trafiony rezultat
                    {% else %}
                    Nietrafiony
                    {% endif %}
                </td>
            </tr>
            {% endwith_ %}
            {% endwith_ %}
            {% endwith_ %}
            {% else %}
            <tr>
                <td>{{ bet.match.home_team }}</td>
                <td>{{ bet.home_team_score }}</td>
                <td>{{ bet.away_team_score }}</td>
                <td>{{ bet.match.away_team }}</td>
                <td class="wrong-result">No Result</td>
            </tr>
            {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <p>Czarny ko:
            {% if data.underdog %}
            <span class="{% if data.underdog.team == selected_winner %}exact{% else %}wrong-result{% endif %}"><strong>{{ data.underdog.team }}</strong></span>
            {% else %}
            <span><strong>Brak wyboru</strong></span>
        </p>
        {% endif %}

        <p>Krl strzelcw:
            {% if data.top_scorer %}
            <span class="{% if data.top_scorer.player == selected_top_scorer %}exact{% else %}wrong-result{% endif %}"><strong>{{ data.top_scorer.player }}</strong></span>
            {% else %}
            <span><strong>Brak wyboru</strong></span>
        </p>
        {% endif %}

        <p>Zwycizca turnieju:
            {% if data.tournament_winner %}
            <span class="{% if data.tournament_winner.team == selected_winner %}exact{% else %}wrong-result{% endif %}"><strong>{{ data.tournament_winner.team }}</strong></span>
            {% else %}
            <span><strong>Brak wyboru</strong></span>
        </p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
    <hr>
    {% endfor %}
</div>
{% endblock %}
```

